Just a bit of css cleanup: 
```css
<style>
  body {
    font-family: sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    background-color: white;
  }
  .topbar {
    background-color: #996189;
    width: 100%;
    color: white;
  }
  .topbar h1 {
    font-size: x-large;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-left: 32px;
  }
  .content-container {
    padding: 32px;
  }
</style>
```
